divs: Sighting DetailsWe Have encountered many ships in the Salt Lake city area. We have many pictures. A very active area. We also back in 2005 were abducted my Husband and I. This ship my husband noticed in the west sky of Salt Lake City. With are previous experiences throughout the years we knew exactly what we were seeing. A giant ball of light hovering over Utah's west desert dwarfed all in coming commercial airlines. It had been a few years since we had any sightings of UFO in are area.We were excited. Then it was gone.
